            "id": 5966117,
            "title": "盤中速報 - Alphabet公司(C)(GOOG-US)大跌5.04%，報156.87美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Alphabet公司(C)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GOOG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GOOG-US</a>)截至台北時間07日23:07股價下跌8.33美元，報156.87美元，跌幅5.04%，成交量11,509,958（股），盤中最高價166.98美元、最低價156.76美元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.45%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.04%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.37%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.41%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Alphabet公司(C)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GOOG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GOOG-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+1.94%</li> <li>近 1 月：+11.82%</li> <li>近 3 月：-14.54%</li> <li>近 6 月：-7.36%</li> <li>今年以來：-13.25%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/5966117",
